{"tid":1519943,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"法律上真係無得脫離家人關係？","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:35:26.000Z","uid":2719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"842f3fa66ddf87c08eb6a1b346b19efe7a7c1485","tid":1519943,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:24:51.000Z","msg":"「不要勸導，學術台非感情台」<br />\n<br />\n上網查過，聲名又好、律師信都好，都係無法律效應。<br />\n只係得公告作用，例如叫財政公司唔好煩你。<br />\n<br />\n原來連斷絕關係嘅自由都無，民主？<br />\n咩搬走改聯絡電話咪得，我知。<br />\n但咁同條女講我養你唔結婚咪得一樣，想求個心安理得啫。<br />\n<br />\n有無有法律效力嘅脫離方法可以教我，<br />\n唔想再聽到你係我個仔乜柒啲說話，同叫我中國人一樣咁難接受。"},{"pid":"f46316c6224f4534816dbb1e9373401257344866","tid":1519943,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=c8bb3bdb\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=a1bb6e77\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=56bb83b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d084d828c3c2c49cb40a4637cf8fa3892edc764c","tid":1519943,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\